663
00:35:23,140 --> 00:35:27,280
 dopusti da se Bog u tvom životu proslavi.

664
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:29,580
 To je na što smo pozvani

665
00:35:29,580 --> 00:35:32,000
 u razlučivanju.

666
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:34,180
 Da postanemo djeca Božja,

667
00:35:34,180 --> 00:35:36,820
 da preuzmemo stvari u svoje ruke

668
00:35:36,820 --> 00:35:38,260
 i da rastemo.

669
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:40,740
 Možda ću često donositi krive odluke,

670
00:35:41,700 --> 00:35:44,780
 ali iz tih krivih odluka učimo.

671
00:35:44,780 --> 00:35:49,780
 Imajte hrabrosti,

672
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:50,780
 molite se,

673
00:35:50,780 --> 00:35:51,640
 tišina,

674
00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:53,380
 sve to pismo.

675
00:35:53,380 --> 00:35:54,600
 Imamo sve,

676
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:57,900
 sva oružja,

677
00:35:57,900 --> 00:35:59,680
 sve alate koje nam crkva daje,

678
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:01,000
 sakramenti.

679
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:02,900
 I druga stvar,

680
00:36:02,900 --> 00:36:03,700
 nismo sami.

681
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:05,100
 Kad donosiš odluku,

682
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:05,800
 nisi sam.

683
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:08,000
 Imaš mudre ljude oko sebe.

684
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,420
 Pitaj za savjet,

685
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:10,840
 oni će ti pomoći.

686
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:12,160
 nemoj se bojati, pitati.

687
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:14,600
 I tako se donose odluke.

688
00:36:14,600 --> 00:36:16,120
 Skupi informacije

689
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:17,480
 o onome,

690
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:19,120
 o predmetu u kojem donosiš.

691
00:36:19,120 --> 00:36:20,140
 I onda razmotri.

692
00:36:20,140 --> 00:36:21,880
 Evo, s tim bih završio.

693
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:23,600
 Ne bih više duljio.

694
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:26,720
 Ovo me možete čitati

695
00:36:26,720 --> 00:36:28,080
 i u knjigama

696
00:36:28,080 --> 00:36:28,880
 o razlučivanju,

697
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:29,460
 u duhovama,

698
00:36:29,460 --> 00:36:30,740
 ali ovo je ključno

699
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:32,360
 u razlučivanju.

700
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,700
 Amen.

701
00:36:40,220 --> 00:36:41,220
 Hvala.

